						               													<description>Wild West Chronicles&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This easy-to-learn and intuitive game system will soon have you simulating gunfights between outlaws, raids alone the Mexican border, Indian ambushes and many other other situations that are typical of the Far West.&amp;#10;These rules include army lists for desperados, Texas rangers, lawmen, outlaws, town-peoples and Indians.&amp;#10;Each model has a points value that depends on his skills and weaponry so you can create well-balanced scenarios that all the players can enjoy.&amp;#10;the use of the table has been reduced to a minimum and the whole system revolves around the addition and subtraction of six-dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are three standard scenarios inside:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     the gunfight, &amp;#10;     the rescue and &amp;#10;     the ambush!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There is also a simple system to help you track the experience of your squads from one gunfight to another.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you enjoy the wild west setting then this game for You!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
